This package installs the current prebuilt DAPHNE userspace runtime into the
PetaLinux image.

Installed payload:
- `/usr/bin/daphneServer`
- `/usr/bin/hermes_udp_srv`
- private runtime libraries under `/usr/lib/daphne-server`
- `BUILD-METADATA.txt` describing the staged source bundle

Source of truth today:
- a staged runtime tarball harvested from a working board
- `scripts/petalinux/stage_runtime_into_project.sh`

Design intent:
- keep the package layout independent of `/home/petalinux`
- preserve deterministic runtime libraries via a private libdir
- let the service layer start `daphneServer` and Hermes from normal system
  paths
